17.Find region-wise total quantity sold by each salesperson.

mysql> select salesperson,region,count(quantity) from Sales group by region,salesperson;
+-------------+--------+-----------------+
| salesperson | region | count(quantity) |
+-------------+--------+-----------------+
| Alice       | North  |               4 |
| Bob         | South  |               3 |
| Charlie     | East   |               3 |
| David       | West   |               2 |
| Eve         | South  |               3 |
+-------------+--------+-----------------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)

18.Find salespersons who made more than 3 transactions and total sales amount is over $1000.

mysql> select salesperson,count(salesperson),sum(saleamount) from Sales group by Salesperson having sum(saleamount)>1000 and count(salesperson)>3;
+-------------+--------------------+-----------------+
| salesperson | count(salesperson) | sum(saleamount) |
+-------------+--------------------+-----------------+
| Alice       |                  4 |         1410.00 |
+-------------+--------------------+-----------------+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)

19.Find average sale amount per region and show only regions with average above $200.

mysql> select region,avg(saleamount) from Sales group by region;
