| region | avg(saleamount) |
+--------+-----------------+
| North  |      352.500000 |
| South  |      333.333333 |
| East   |      700.000000 |
| West   |      600.000000 |
+--------+-----------------+
4 rows in set (0.00 sec)

20.List regions and products where more than 3 units were sold.

mysql> select product,region from Sales group by product,region having sum(quantity)>3;
+---------+--------+
| product | region |
+---------+--------+
| Mouse   | South  |
| Monitor | South  |
| Mouse   | West   |
+---------+--------+
